130
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,900
 A ne samo gospodin Trump.

131
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:28,560
 To je činio gospodin Biden.

132
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:31,760
 To je činila i administracija

133
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:33,540
